data.description: Welcome to a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that effortlessly combines practicality with comfort. The kitchen takes center stage, offering a spacious eat-in area with a nook featuring window seating and ample natural light. The bedrooms provide quiet retreats, with an updated bathroom servicing the living spaces.  Entertain guests with a spacious finished basement w/ bar area as well as another full bathroom.  Plenty of added storage in the unfinished area and don't miss out on the extra large back yard perfect for a growing family! Conveniently located near the highway, this residence ensures an easy and straightforward commute. This home is designed to balance everyday functionality with a touch of comfort.
